headline: How Boeing is quietly betting on a ‘brilliant’ 39-year old engineer—and setting the stage for a turnaround
summary: Brian Yutko wowed his peers at MIT and his colleagues at flying-taxi startup Wisk. But can he help rebuild new product leadership at Boeing?
